Subject: Setup Netwrix Auditor
Description: I was informed that we have access to Netwrix Auditor and we do not have it setup. I have downloaded it and tried to set it up from the article but it is not working. Can I get assistance setting this up?
Solution_Comment__c: Customer is not licensed for NA. I'd informed them this information is available through NEA via the AD Activity auditing. I also provided information on the freeware tool, Netwrix Account Lockout Examiner, and let them know that while it is not a supported product, it may assist them in their investigations.
